INSTRUCTIONS:

Create a 'Mobile_Poll__c' record with a question, then create several answers as child records ('Mobile_Poll_Answer__c').

Go to the Mobile Poll detail page, click on the 'Mobile Poll Page' button and vote!

Go to the Chatter Homepage to see the link post that was created!


I tried to keep the code footprint as small and tidy as possible. Additionally I tried to use as much of the standardController functionality as possible.

